ul.li:
Bold emphasized text -
                emphasizes the selected text by surrounding it with <emphasis
                    role="bold"/> tag;

Italic emphasized text -
                emphasizes the selected text by surrounding it with <emphasis
                    role="italic"/> tag;

Insert a variable list
                    at the caret position - inserts a DocBook variable list. A child
                list item is also inserted automatically by default;

Insert a procedure
               - inserts a DocBook procedure element. A step
                   child item is also inserted automatically;
